OrientDB is a document-graph database written in Java with no dependencies other than Java 6 or greater.

***

###Features
* ACID transactions
* Indexing
* Rich documents with JSON syntax
* SQL support
* HTTP REST protocol using JSON
* Embeddable
* Lightweight
* So many more
